  "description": "<p><strong>Windows 8.1带来了许多根据消费者的反馈而来的新功能，其中便包括完全重新设计过的搜索体验。据微软表示，改进Windows 8.1中的搜索体验，是他们的一个重要目标。</strong>微软重新设计过的Search Charm，可以\"无处不在\"地进行搜索，包括用户的PC、云端和互联网。在未来，该公司还计划在Metro/Modern应用中添加搜索支持。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ef10afd/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245415.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9BWindows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245415.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9BWindows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245415.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9BWindows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245415.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9BWindows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?